{"tid":1409373,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"只係扯高咗條裙姐","createTime":"2019-08-04T20:46:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T16:24:17.000Z","uid":15379,"like":67,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"75e336177e2cec768eb40fdd9e83e60c4c2aecc9","tid":1409373,"uid":15379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T20:46:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我屌你老母#150753</span></span><br />\n有片有人證幾百萬人睇撚住女仔點樣被班畜生凌辱，你同我懶係客觀咁分析解話。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我屌你老母兩次啦！</span></span>你仲賤撚過CCTVB班仆街高層啊！！<br />\n我比你退一萬步，唔係，就算係一億步來講，你覺得扯高條裙就冇問題，叫做可以接受咩？？？<br />\n<br />\n你一係就五毛，一係就閪狗藍絲，如果你係偽中立犬儒撚或者同路人，<span style=\"color: red;\">你就重撚仆街冚家剷</span>，大事大非前係到粉飾太平，轉移視線。<br />\n<br />\n或者你係想手足唔好比仇恨沖昏頭腦，做錯事，但都唔係比你用咩扯高條裙呢啲講法輕輕帶過嘅理由啊！！！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">事實就係班仆街閪狗冇人性啊！！！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">屌你老母三次啊！！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">反省可你自己啦！！<br />\n<br />\n撚樣！！</span></span>"},{"pid":"af2cf30e78b6d1306534e8ae9fb247ece036f644","tid":1409373,"uid":15379,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T20:47:12.000Z","msg":"反省吓，嬲撚到字都打撚錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c60ee568cabf44485781c19aed444beb03d9b226","tid":1409373,"uid":15379,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T20:50:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">非禮及意圖強姦<br />\n高處暗位開鎗暗殺</span></span>"},{"pid":"e269ddb0654881d2b2749697693c820498adb914","tid":1409373,"uid":226955,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T20:50:53.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n#為避免運動將來可能分裂，凝聚民間對於「五大訴求缺一不可」嘅共識，係文宣重中之重嘅長期目標<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">#毋忘葉虎事件！（疑似中聯辦指揮黑社會打人）大家可以幫推，甚至可以做埋社區文宣煲大佢，絕對唔可以比呢單野不了了之！</span><br />\n［緊急］點解葉虎單嘢可以不了了之？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1382778\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1382778</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">#仲有84比海綿子彈爆頭暈倒義士、83有義士比狗圍住唔比食哮喘藥結果腦缺氧暈倒，728上環比橡膠子彈爆頭暈倒義士，希望你地可以平安萬全</span>"},{"pid":"31a9d2b72826bd3f909d2158b74f0154960fd7a7","tid":1409373,"uid":15379,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T20:51:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">非禮及意圖強姦<br />\n高處暗位開鎗暗殺</span></span>"},{"pid":"f04a8a9a87357393efe6073a5109d23abb993289","tid":1409373,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T20:51:32.000Z","msg":"天滅中共<br />\n五毛死全家<br />\n黑警死全家"},{"pid":"6356a755d917f0dc573393397e65f2739c97df2c","tid":1409373,"uid":15379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T20:54:55.000Z","msg":"非禮及意圖強姦<br />\n高處暗位開鎗暗殺<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\"></span></span>"},{"pid":"251c10293ded67ed405ebc4bd83d2959f4c010ab","tid":1409373,"uid":15379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T20:55:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">非禮及意圖強姦<br />\n高處暗位開鎗暗殺</span></span>"},{"pid":"14e873190ee55701aa01dd89d9ea06c3feea396f","tid":1409373,"uid":15379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T20:57:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">非禮及意圖強姦<br />\n高處暗位開鎗暗殺</span></span>"},{"pid":"e79f734d3201691cadc3ec4ac215cd44b23223ff","tid":1409373,"uid":15379,"like":0,